弃”的意思，这里指被贬谪。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>“怀旧空吟闻笛赋”中“空”是“空洞”的意思。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>“暂凭杯酒长精神”中“暂”是“暂且”的意思。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>“沉舟侧畔千帆过”中“畔”是“旁边”的意思。</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>&nbsp;下列对诗歌中加点词理解有误的一项是（ &nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "5036342747", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "70977d23-267b-417e-b3c8-a08064603f63", "global_title": {"zh-CN": " 下列对诗歌中加点词理解有误的一项是（  ）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<p>&nbsp;下列对诗歌中加点词理解有误的一项是（ &nbsp;）</p>\n"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status": "ready", "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/70977d23-267b-417e-b3c8-a08064603f63@1.pkg/1772602093019/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602094106", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/70977d23-267b-417e-b3c8-a08064603f63@1.pkg/1772602093019/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602094106"}, "auto_fill_thumb": true, "prom_resouce_type": "questions", "qb_year": "2025", "n